Triggermail
===========

XXX THIS MODULE IS NOW DEPRECATED.
XXX Use the Sailthru::Client module instead.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Digest::MD5
HTTP::Request
JSON::XS
LWP
LWP::Protocol::https
Params::Validate
URI::Escape

